**Analysis:**

The text contains 108 words (excluding punctuation).
The number of long words (words with more than 6 letters) is 64.
The number of sentences is 5.

**LIX Calculator:**

LIX = ((Words / Sentences) + (Long words / Words)) * 100
LIX = ((108 / 5) + (64 / 108)) * 100
LIX = (21.6 + 0.59) * 100
LIX = 22.19 * 100
**LIX = 22**